title: Kid Made Modern DIY Snow Globe Kit
description:
Create a winter wonderland that will last all year long! Turn it into a family affair and help your little one create a snow globe that celebrates the most wonderful time of the year. Makes a great gift. Recommended for ages 6 and up. Includes:

  • 6 colorful clays for molding
  • 3 plastic clay tools
  • Assorted sequins
  • 2 glitter vials
  • white glue - .69 fl oz (20 mL)
  • 1 snowman figurine
  • 1 snow globe
  • 1 pipette
